wmiirc-lua (0.2.8-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * move to ~/.wmii-lua, switch to github for hosting, build chnages for
    handling submodules in ext dir, less dependency on lua version and wmii
    version, improve installaction and start scripts, added view_workdir
    plugin, using wimenu if available, many misc bugs fixed.

